Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.44,0:00:02.67,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Thirty years ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.23,0:00:05.94,Character Card,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,0)}Shoudou Kurumi (39)\NHead of the Shoudou Family
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.76,0:00:05.94,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Shoudou Kurumi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} befriended a boy by the sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.45,0:00:11.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ultimately, that boy saved her life in a traffic incident.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.15,0:00:15.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When Kurumi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} won 100 million yen on a chance lottery ticket...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.65,0:00:17.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She decided to give it to that boy instead...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.82,0:00:19.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And announced it in magazines and on TV.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.82,0:00:23.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The clues were: Her memories of those summer days...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.74,0:00:27.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As well as the large scar the boy received while rescuing her.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.37,0:00:31.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Two men came forward claiming to be the boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.17,0:00:34.09,Character Card,,0,0,0,,{\fad(210,210)}Kusumoto Ryuuhei (42)
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.82,0:00:33.99,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Kusumoto Ryuuhei{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} had a scar on his back...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.63,0:00:36.51,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,While Banba Sougo{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s was on his chest.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.51,0:00:39.39,Character Card,,0,0,0,,{\fad(210,210)}Banba Sougo (41)
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.56,0:00:38.90,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Both were shaped like the number 1.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.13,0:00:42.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In order to ascertain which was truly the one...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.80,0:00:44.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We decided to go along to the Shoudou estate.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.51,0:00:46.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But there...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.51,0:00:49.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Outside that very house, investigating a\Nserial murderer from many years ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.72,0:00:52.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Were detectives from the first division, watching secretly.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.48,0:00:57.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The criminal from that time also has a 1-shaped scar on his body.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.53,0:01:00.99,Character Card,,0,0,0,,{\fad(210,0)}Houya Taisuke (40)\NButler
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.24,0:00:58.98,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.01,0:01:04.08,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,It was soon discovered that the butler of the estate,\NHouya Taisuke{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, also has a scar on his back.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.80,0:01:08.64,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Of them, which is truly the "Boy of Memory"?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.56,0:01:12.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Love is eternal, labyrinths are mysterious.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.58,0:01:14.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Saturday nights are for mystery!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.98,0:01:16.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,With the deadline approaching, it's time to identify the first love!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.96,0:01:19.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The scar case takes an unexpected turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.58,0:01:21.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Perceiving the one and only truth...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.11,0:01:22.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The appearance of a child and the intellect of an adult...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.98,0:01:24.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His name is: Detective Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.33,0:03:13.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.49,0:03:17.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's a scar on the butler's back as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.54,0:03:18.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.79,0:03:21.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Compared to those of Kusumoto{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} and Banba{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.21,0:03:24.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's short and only about 15 cm in length.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.92,0:03:30.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This also suggests that the butler,\NHouya{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, could be the serial murderer.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.89,0:03:31.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.97,0:03:34.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wasn't the serial killer's scar a big one?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.01,0:03:40.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, the superintendent couldn't exactly see well\Nat the time, after just being injured by the culprit.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.90,0:03:45.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He wasn't in a position to accurately estimate the length of the scar.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.07,0:03:50.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Not to mention, it seems the murderer is quite a cautious person.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.24,0:03:57.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After the superintendent cut him,\Nthe culprit did escape by car, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.45,0:04:03.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When the police discovered the car later, there\Nwere absolutely no signs of fingerprints or blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.92,0:04:07.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since the driver's side seat cover had been peeled off...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.38,0:04:10.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His blood had probably gotten on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.26,0:04:12.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why he must have wiped away the fingerprints afterwards.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.93,0:04:17.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, why are you already suspecting the butler is the murderer?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.27,0:04:25.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If someone were that cautious, it isn't like they could\Nbe lured in with moneyâ€”even if the scars were similar.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.52,0:04:33.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even though they could tell the blood had been wiped\Naway, there was no reaction at all from luminol testing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.12,0:04:35.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Those three scars...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.45,0:04:39.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kusumoto{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s is on his back.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.70,0:04:41.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Banba{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} has one on his chest.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.29,0:04:44.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, there's the small one on Houya{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s back.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.10,0:04:47.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As children...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.17,0:04:50.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kusomoto{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} was thin, and Banba{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} loved to study.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.05,0:04:55.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The boy of memory was familiar with both the sea and fish...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.47,0:04:57.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His favorite drink was ginger ale.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.31,0:05:00.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He loved to eat sushi and fried noodles...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.56,0:05:03.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As for his character, he was honest.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.94,0:05:06.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He was known to his classmates as...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.07,0:05:08.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Gari?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.49,0:05:10.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.99,0:05:14.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How is it going?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.28,0:05:15.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The investigation.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.70,0:05:17.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, no...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.20,0:05:18.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm not quite sure yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.45,0:05:20.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.83,0:05:22.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, there is still time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.71,0:05:26.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A midnight snack has been prepared, so, should you like...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.96,0:05:27.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Midnight snack?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.59,0:05:30.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could that be...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.76,0:05:32.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sushi maybe?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.13,0:05:33.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.34,0:05:35.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's impressive, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.30,0:05:37.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, how about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.43,0:05:40.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is a secret, though, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.23,0:05:43.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A little lower.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.86,0:05:50.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's he saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.15,0:05:54.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, I can count on you for the rest?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.74,0:05:58.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, I'm surprised...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.33,0:06:06.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was under the impression you were a short\Nhigh schooler whose voice hadn't changed yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.92,0:06:09.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But to think you're just a little boy...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.42,0:06:13.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's as if Sherlock Holmes were imitating a child.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.26,0:06:15.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.01,0:06:19.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm able to see that which others cannot.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.89,0:06:23.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, I'll be waiting in my room.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.85,0:06:25.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll leave the rest to you...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.27,0:06:29.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mr. Detective.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.11,0:06:30.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.11,0:06:37.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As delicious as expected!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.20,0:06:44.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mr. Butler, do you want to join us?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.25,0:06:47.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That lady said you should eat, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.08,0:06:49.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.26,0:07:00.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Natural ingredients really do taste the best.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.89,0:07:02.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, this is manufactured.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.10,0:07:04.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What're you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.64,0:07:06.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course it's natural!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.52,0:07:08.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You agree with me, don't you, Detective?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.15,0:07:10.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.61,0:07:11.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you ask me...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.23,0:07:15.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.82,0:07:19.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're wondering whether it's natural or manufactured?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.11,0:07:21.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That doesn't matter!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.45,0:07:23.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Doesn't matter"?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.33,0:07:26.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, I'd say it's important...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.25,0:07:29.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now, nowâ€”you see, the boy of memory...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.62,0:07:33.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's been said he knew the sea and fish well, and loved sushi.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.80,0:07:36.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why you thought you could appeal to me with this, no?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.42,0:07:38.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.42,0:07:39.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, it wouldn't be impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.13,0:07:43.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That 100 million yen would be enticing enough to try anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.81,0:07:45.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Speaking of sushi...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.22,0:07:48.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What happened when the boy bought the packed sushi?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.44,0:07:53.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I received 100 yen in excess change,\Nso I went back to the shop to return it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.90,0:07:57.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's in my nature to not keep what isn't mine, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.74,0:07:59.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's pretty strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.53,0:08:01.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What is?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.53,0:08:06.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, that honest boy that returns\Neverything that doesn't belong to him...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.95,0:08:10.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If the chance arose for him to get\N100 million yen from someone else...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.12,0:08:12.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do you think he'd take it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.71,0:08:16.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What're you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.80,0:08:22.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was all because of the help I gave her after\Nwhat happened in that accident back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.01,0:08:25.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She wanted to express her appreciation with the 100 million yen!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.18,0:08:28.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's wrong with coming and accepting it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.89,0:08:31.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You saw it yourself in the bath, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.31,0:08:33.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The big scar I got from that accident!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.98,0:08:34.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.77,0:08:38.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I owe the scar on my back to that accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.61,0:08:43.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's true that you both have large scars of around 30 cm in length.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.78,0:08:48.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, what brings questions of doubt to my mind is exactly that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.20,0:08:54.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Didn't the lady say it in the interview?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.13,0:08:56.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"The scar reached from one side to the other," were her words.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.21,0:09:02.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She didn't say much else, but she was certain it was a big scar.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.01,0:09:05.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And, about how old were you at the time?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.64,0:09:09.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was in around my second or third year of school...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.64,0:09:10.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.68,0:09:13.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you were in your second or third year at the time...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.14,0:09:17.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The scar would have only been around 15 cm long.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.40,0:09:19.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, see...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.57,0:09:22.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When I first got the scar, it was about that size.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.61,0:09:27.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As I grew up, the scar got bigger as I did...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.41,0:09:28.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.66,0:09:30.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You didn't know?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.12,0:09:34.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That scar wouldn't increase in size no matter how much you grew.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.37,0:09:35.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What!?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.50,0:09:39.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If a scar is 15 cm at the time...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.34,0:09:41.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It should stay 15 cm until death.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.63,0:09:42.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.84,0:09:45.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I just had a big physique is all.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.30,0:09:46.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Same with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.76,0:09:48.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, Kusumoto{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.72,0:09:52.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I recall you mentioning being thin in your childhood.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.19,0:09:54.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.65,0:10:02.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I bet that, when you heard the boy of memory's\Nname was Gari, you mistook what it meant.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.24,0:10:03.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You took it as garigari, for "skin and bones."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.70,0:10:08.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Gari is actually for gariben, "someone who studies hard."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.08,0:10:11.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Gari from gariben, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.70,0:10:14.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.08,0:10:19.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When the boy from her memories ate fried noodles by the sea...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.09,0:10:21.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He heaped a pile of red ginger on top of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.38,0:10:23.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.09,0:10:25.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've never heard that before!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.47,0:10:28.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It should come as no surprise that you haven't.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.14,0:10:33.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is a new story that she only just told me today.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.43,0:10:36.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You still don't see it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.02,0:10:40.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The boy of memory that loved ginger ale...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.69,0:10:42.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Bought packed sushi often...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.44,0:10:46.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And heaped red ginger on his fried noodles...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.61,0:10:47.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.74,0:10:50.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That boy liked ginger, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.83,0:10:53.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ginger is one of the key ingredients in ginger ale...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.66,0:10:57.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And the Gari that goes with sushi is pickled\Nginger that results from soaking it in vinegar!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.71,0:11:01.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, does that mean that boy got the Gari from...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.50,0:11:02.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.09,0:11:06.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The boy with a fondness for ginger was known as Gari.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.09,0:11:08.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.76,0:11:10.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The one who didn't eye any other sushi...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.26,0:11:13.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But went straight for the ginger...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.56,0:11:15.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The butler, Houya Taisuke{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.02,0:11:19.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.06,0:11:20.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The real guy was here!?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.02,0:11:22.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.19,0:11:26.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's a scar on his back about 15 cm in length.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.07,0:11:28.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm not mistaken, am I!?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.49,0:11:31.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, why didn't you say something!?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.12,0:11:32.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You could have got 100 million!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.62,0:11:37.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That money is something I could never accept.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.87,0:11:41.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If I had not told her, "Stay here," back then...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.34,0:11:45.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She wouldn't have been involved in that accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.30,0:11:49.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Therefore, I decided to support in secret...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.68,0:11:52.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, it seems you weren't able to do it in secret, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.97,0:11:55.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't you see?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.85,0:12:01.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Given that she clearly knew you wouldn't\Naccept something that wasn't your own...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.02,0:12:05.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't it obvious as to why she announced\Nshe'd give you 100 million on TV?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.15,0:12:11.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She wanted the one by her side to come out and tell her.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.16,0:12:16.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She wanted you to tell her before any impersonators appeared!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.54,0:12:21.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, that lady really did already...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.08,0:12:22.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, she'd already discovered it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.42,0:12:27.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She knew that the butler, Houya{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, was the boy from her memory.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.38,0:12:32.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The reason she had you see to my back in the\Nbath, even with the broken air conditioning...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.14,0:12:36.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And her reason for withholding the red ginger story...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.72,0:12:38.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As well as why she had sushi prepared for a midnight snack...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.27,0:12:41.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They were all just hints for me to follow.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.48,0:12:43.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.23,0:12:44.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What will you do now, Houya{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.65,0:12:47.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The lady is waiting in her room.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.99,0:12:52.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.86,0:12:53.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.03,0:12:54.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.87,0:12:57.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's all right!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.83,0:13:00.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll go tell her in your place if you want!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.33,0:13:04.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Or would you like for me to tell her?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.71,0:13:10.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I know she wouldn't want these two that came\Njust for the money to use her precious memory.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.18,0:13:14.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.14,0:13:15.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I understand!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.47,0:13:16.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll tell her myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.77,0:13:27.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Seems we were able to push him well, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.73,0:13:28.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.32,0:13:29.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Geez...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.69,0:13:35.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,With my situation as it is, I couldn't tell the truth even if I wanted...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.61,0:13:37.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Were you saying something?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.70,0:13:41.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's Kamen Yaiba!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.70,0:13:43.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It'd be terrible if his identity were revealed!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.58,0:13:46.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, I'll just...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.38,0:13:48.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You know...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.09,0:13:53.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please wait just a moment longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.51,0:13:55.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The police?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.22,0:13:57.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We were just joking!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.80,0:14:01.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I got this scar on my chest while surfing a long time ago, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.18,0:14:01.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.27,0:14:06.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Our business is with the one with the big scar on his back...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.65,0:14:07.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.94,0:14:10.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As for that scar...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.86,0:14:13.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Some twenty years ago, there was a serial killer...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.61,0:14:16.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who, after being cornered by Superintendent Matsumoto...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.28,0:14:20.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ended up with a 1-shaped scar on his back from a katana.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.29,0:14:26.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I couldn't remember whether it was on the back or the front at first.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.67,0:14:28.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, with the mail from Mouri, it all became clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.25,0:14:30.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mail?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.17,0:14:32.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, man...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.63,0:14:34.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I forgot to return Uncle's phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.26,0:14:40.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Normally, when someone is injured,\Nthey'll cover the wound with their hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.76,0:14:46.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,However, there was no reaction on the steering\Nwheel when we tried the luminol test, because...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.31,0:14:49.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His hand couldn't reach the wound.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.02,0:14:53.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In other words, it was on his back.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.82,0:15:01.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You pulled off the cover on the driver's\Nseat to get rid of the blood, did you not?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.03,0:15:03.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.20,0:15:03.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's not it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.04,0:15:08.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I met a guy a long time ago that had a scar\Non his back, and I thought it was cool...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.46,0:15:09.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, I just copied him!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.17,0:15:12.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Enough with the random excuses!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.84,0:15:14.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's true!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.00,0:15:15.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please, believe me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.42,0:15:18.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And, did this man happen to be whistling?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.05,0:15:19.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did he?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.51,0:15:20.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.30,0:15:23.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I think it was...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.85,0:15:26.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A song that was popular like, twenty years ago!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.73,0:15:28.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is this the truth?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.73,0:15:29.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.02,0:15:30.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Superintendent...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.44,0:15:34.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A song that was popular twenty years ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.98,0:15:37.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The song of the serial killer...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.54,0:15:48.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His name is Kusumoto Ryuuhei, 42 years old.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.83,0:15:54.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The incident dates back to fifteen years\Nago, when he was homestaying abroad.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.17,0:15:57.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We were able to verify it, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.13,0:15:59.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He can be removed from the list of possible suspects.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.76,0:16:00.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.84,0:16:07.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He came across the man in question at a\Nsauna, just before leaving for his homestay.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.43,0:16:12.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There was a towel covering his face, so he wasn't entirely visible.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.65,0:16:17.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"The scar on my back is a badge of courage\Na cop gave me some five years back."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.36,0:16:18.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"You want one too, by any chance?"
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.82,0:16:21.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's what he said, with a laugh.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.82,0:16:23.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And that sauna?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.49,0:16:26.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sato and Takagi have just gone to make inquiries.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.45,0:16:29.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tell them to be on their guard.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.21,0:16:30.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.62,0:16:33.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Two victims twenty years ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.33,0:16:35.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,One victim fifteen years ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.13,0:16:37.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's three victims he's claimed...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.05,0:16:38.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's a ruthless criminal.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.80,0:16:41.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, there's one more.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.05,0:16:43.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Have you forgotten?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.76,0:16:46.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How could I forget?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.18,0:16:50.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Superintendent Morimura, who was\Nkilled in the line of the duty on that case.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.81,0:16:55.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He was the man who taught me the\Nfundamentals of being a police officer.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.20,0:17:05.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Superintendent Morimura...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.41,0:17:12.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even after being promoted two classes\Nahead after you died in the line of duty...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.87,0:17:14.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I still don't understand...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.87,0:17:16.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What you meant back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.96,0:17:19.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Matsumoto...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.63,0:17:22.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's something...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.63,0:17:24.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His whistling...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.14,0:17:28.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's definitely something to it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.43,0:17:34.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just what did you mean, Morimura?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.06,0:17:39.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And we ended up with nothing for our effort.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.94,0:17:41.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's nothing that can be done.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.82,0:17:44.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The case was fifteen years ago, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.36,0:17:45.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.41,0:17:49.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The building's been renovated, and\Nthe class of customers have changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.45,0:17:54.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, there's a large remodeled spa on 5th\Nstreet that everyone is saying is great!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.25,0:17:55.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Really now?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.29,0:17:59.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why don't you head over there with Chiba{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.59,0:18:02.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'd rather go alone...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.97,0:18:04.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.51,0:18:05.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Were you inviting me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.14,0:18:08.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course I was!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.64,0:18:09.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, how about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.64,0:18:13.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If we catch the serial killer before the deadline...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.09,0:18:15.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The two of us will go to the hot spring.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.56,0:18:18.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, there's only three days...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.90,0:18:20.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Take me to the hot spring!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.36,0:18:22.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.44,0:18:23.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is this really all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.99,0:18:27.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Police officers being so lovey-dovey while on duty.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.37,0:18:30.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We weren't being lovey-dovey...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.41,0:18:33.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We're here asking about...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.66,0:18:37.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't reveal too much to the children!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.79,0:18:38.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're right...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.88,0:18:39.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.92,0:18:42.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To summarize the case from what's been on TV...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.50,0:18:45.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Along with the story I heard from Superintendent Matsumoto...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.42,0:18:47.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The first case occurred twenty years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.14,0:18:53.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The victim was a 50 year-old doctor: Boukawa Tsuguharu{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.10,0:18:56.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The murder weapon was the Japanese sword from his house.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.06,0:18:58.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just two days later, the next victim was...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.27,0:19:01.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,An associate professor of science and engineering at Tohto University...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.86,0:19:04.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The 42 year-old Mugita Atsunori{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.32,0:19:05.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The weapon was the same sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.49,0:19:09.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, while a detective was questioning him...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.28,0:19:12.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There was a driver that appeared suspicious\Nthat ended up suddenly driving off.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.33,0:19:16.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The detective on duty was struck by the car, and died.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.25,0:19:21.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After he caught up with the car, Superintendent\NMatsumoto was attacked by the culprit...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.92,0:19:23.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And even though his left eye was injured...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.80,0:19:26.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He took the katana from his attacker and cut him across his back.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.92,0:19:29.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As a result, a 1-shaped scar was left behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.51,0:19:31.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And five years later...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.43,0:19:37.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nabei Susumu{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, a 34 year-old lawyer, was\Nkilled with a kitchen knife from his own home.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.98,0:19:39.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His method.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.06,0:19:41.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Render them unconscious with a stun gun...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.27,0:19:44.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And then cruelly slice at their bodies with swords and bladed weapons.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.61,0:19:49.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In all three home cases, there were no signs of break-ins...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.61,0:19:52.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Which led police to believe it was an acquaintance, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.03,0:19:57.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The case went cold because no common points\Ncould be found to connect the three victims.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.66,0:19:58.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, I'm right, aren't!?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.83,0:20:00.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.71,0:20:03.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, I still don't get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.04,0:20:08.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The first and second victims died by the same weapon,\Nwhich is why it's assumed they share a perpetrator, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.42,0:20:09.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.63,0:20:11.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The case five years later involved a kitchen knife.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.51,0:20:14.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How do you know it was the same offender?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.06,0:20:16.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, no, that's...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.35,0:20:17.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's because...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.50,0:20:19.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All of the victims had the same letter cut into...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.02,0:20:20.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait, Sato{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.06,0:20:23.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Weren't you the one who told me to stay quiet about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.15,0:20:25.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.27,0:20:26.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Every time these kids ask...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.09,0:20:32.62,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,With under three days remaining before the\Ndeadline is upon us, do you think he can caught?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.49,0:20:30.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They're broadcasting about it now!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.65,0:20:31.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That case!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.92,0:20:34.89,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Criminal Psychologist, Hiramune{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.00,0:20:39.18,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,With the conditions as they are, let's say that it's highly unlikely.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.46,0:20:42.74,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,The culprit has probably drawn the curtains...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.63,0:20:45.71,Character Card,,0,0,0,,{\fad(210,0)}Hiramune Douji (41)\NCriminal Psychologist
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.79,0:20:44.05,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Unplugged his phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.08,0:20:45.72,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,And isolated himself from the outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.03,0:20:50.88,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,The suspect is likely trembling in bed,\Nwaiting for the deadline to pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.32,0:20:54.47,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,To remain inconspicuous, he'll keep disposing of his safe tiles...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.52,0:20:56.47,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Just waiting for this round to end.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.78,0:20:59.99,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,In the event that isn't the case, come kill me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.28,0:21:05.99,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,If you're prepared to throw away the hardships you've\Nendured while hiding for fifteen years, I mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.73,0:21:08.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I know that man!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.48,0:21:11.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He lives in the same apartment building as I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.57,0:21:15.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, since we're going over to Ayumi's to play today...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.03,0:21:16.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We might get to see him, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.87,0:21:17.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That man there.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.16,0:21:18.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Perhaps.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.79,0:21:21.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.37,0:21:24.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We might come across the serial killer as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.00,0:21:26.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.13,0:21:27.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't come!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.42,0:21:29.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ai{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}, you're scary!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.01,0:21:32.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, have a safe walk home.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.72,0:21:35.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't hesitate to call us if the murderer appears!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.76,0:21:36.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.81,0:21:42.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A letter on the bodies of the victims, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.69,0:21:46.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.90,0:21:49.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You can totally see the buildings way out there!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.82,0:21:52.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The scenery at night must be really great, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.49,0:21:53.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We're home!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.20,0:21:56.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We bought juice!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.20,0:21:58.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And quite a few snacks as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.58,0:22:02.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You bought Yaiba chocolate too?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.37,0:22:03.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.54,0:22:04.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,By the way...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.62,0:22:07.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We happened to pass a strange man near the entrance.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.79,0:22:08.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A strange man?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.63,0:22:14.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was a man who was whistling and wearing an off-season long coat.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.97,0:22:17.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What!?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.43,0:22:19.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What kind of person was this!?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.10,0:22:19.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did you see his face!?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.72,0:22:21.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.52,0:22:23.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He had a beard, and a hat drawn over his face...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.35,0:22:25.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Listen, all of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.39,0:22:28.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Until I get back, don't take a single step out of this room!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.82,0:22:33.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is it possible that guy heard Hiramune{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} speaking on TV...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.92,0:22:35.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And really came after him!?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.70,0:22:37.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The serial killer!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.95,0:24:01.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hiramune{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.62,0:24:05.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The suspect was whistling at the time...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.50,0:24:08.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,While tears poured down his face.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.48,0:24:32.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Next Conan's Hint
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.42,0:24:34.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Letter Z
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.36,0:24:38.85,Signs,,0,0,0,,Look forward to the next episode
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.44,0:24:36.07,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,I'll protect you, Ayumi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.09,0:24:38.07,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Oh? And what about me?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.08,0:24:42.07,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,What now, Mitsuhiko?
